        | you can experience all Florida has to offer from the convenience of your own apartment
      a(href='#' class=' text prominent-text custom-button home-button')
        | book now
    .home-footer
      .text.title-text.centered-text
        | the beach at your front yard
      .separator-text
      .text.body-text
        p.custom-paragraph
          | Completely renovated and decorated with sunny accents, Soleado opens its doos as an
          | alternative to the impersonal an expensive hotel chains in the area where you can stay
          | with family or friends, and embrace what south Florida has to offer.
        p.custom-paragraph
          | Located only a block away from Fort Lauderdale's Beachfront Promenade and sandy beaches,
          | and minutes away from fabulous dining, shopping and nightlife, Soleado Apart Hotel offers
          | the convenience of having your own private apartment while enjoying family-like
          | hospitality eager to make your vacation memorable
    #amenities.amenities
      #amenities-carousel.amenities-back-img.carousel.slide(data-ride='carousel')
        ol.carousel-indicators
          li.active(data-target='#amenities-carousel', data-slide-to='0')
          li(data-target='#amenities-carousel', data-slide-to='1')
          li(data-target='#amenities-carousel', data-slide-to='2')
        .carousel-inner
          .item.active
            img(src='assets/img_amenities_1.jpg')
          .item
            img(src='assets/img_amenities_2.jpg')
          .item
            img(src='assets/img_amenities_3.jpg')
      .amenities-panel
        .text.title-text.centered-text
          | amenities
        .separator-text
        .text.body-text
          p.custom-paragraph
            | What distinguishes our family-run business is the eagerness to make your stay as
            | comfortable as possible while enjoying Florida's tropical weather, great shopping and
            | beautiful Venetian coastline.
          p.custom-paragraph
            | Our premises are designed to make your stay pleasant and uncomplicated. Our pool gets
            | sun at every time of the day for you to sunbathe or kids to play by, or to sit by the
            | lounge areas under the shade of the umbrellas.
          p.custom-paragraph
            | The barbeque area is ready to prepare your favourite meals over charcoal or gas. You can
            | reserve the space and get full service, including cleaning, dish and silverware service
            | (upon request). It accomodates parties up to 16 people.
    .amenities-footer
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-4
        img(src='assets/amenities_bbq.png' class='amenities-img')
        .amenities-gap.text.subtitle-text.centered-text
