    #location.location
      .text.title-text.centered-text
        | where we are located
      .separator-text
      .text.body-text
        p.custom-paragraph
          | Fort Laurerdale is a vibrant and growing coastal city that offers a wide array of
          | activites for all ages. With a beautiful sandy beach almost at your front yard, we are
